<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="referrer" content="no-referrer">
    <title>干员详情 - {{.Char.CharData.Name}}</title>
    <style>
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'NotoSansHans';
            src: url('/assets/font/NotoSansHans-Regular.ttf');
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'NotoSansHans', "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
            background-color: #0f0f0f;
            color: #fff;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        #main {
            width: 1000px;
            height: 600px;
            background: #1a1a1a;
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            padding: 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a 0%, #252525 100%);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
        }

        /* 背景美化 */
        .bg-decoration {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            z-index: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .bg-grid {
            position: absolute;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            background-image: 
                linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 40px 40px;
            transform: rotate(-5deg);
        }

        .bg-glow-1 {
            position: absolute;
            width: 600px;
            height: 600px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 78, 0, 0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
            top: -200px;
            right: -100px;
            filter: blur(50px);
        }

        .bg-glow-2 {
            position: absolute;
            width: 500px;
            height: 500px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0, 150, 255, 0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);
            bottom: -150px;
            left: -100px;
            filter: blur(40px);
        }

        .bg-line {
            position: absolute;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.1), transparent);
            height: 1px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        /* 中间面板：立绘 & 基础信息 */
        .center-panel {
            width: 400px; /* 给中间立绘腾出固定空间 */
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            align-items: center;
            z-index: 10;
            overflow: visible; /* 允许立绘微调溢出但不阻挡侧边 */
        }

        .illustration-container {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 500px; /* 限制立绘容器宽度，防止遮挡侧边点击/显示 */
            height: 100%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: flex-end;
            pointer-events: none; /* 穿透点击，防止阻挡 */
        }

        .illustration {
            height: 110%; /* 立绘高度适当溢出实现冲击感 */
            max-width: none;
            object-fit: contain;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.5));
        }

        .char-base-info {
            width: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(transparent, rgba(0,0,0,0.8) 40%);
            padding: 30px 10px 15px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            z-index: 15;
            position: relative;
        }

        .char-name {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }

        .char-tags {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .tag {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 14px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
        }

        /* 侧边面板 */
        .side-panel {
            width: 280px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 12px;
            z-index: 20;
            height: 100%; /* 确保面板撑满高度 */
        }

        .left-panel { border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); padding-right: 15px; }
        .right-panel { border-left: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); padding-left: 15px; }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .section-title::after {
            content: '';
            flex: 1;
            height: 1px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        }

        /* 属性卡片 */
        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .stat-item {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .stat-label { font-size: 11px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); }
        .stat-value { font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; }

        /* 等级和潜能 */
        .level-potential {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .lv-box { display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 4px; }
        .lv-label { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }
        .lv-val { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 900; }

        .potential-box {
            display: flex;
            gap: 4px;
        }

        .potential-icon-large {
            width: 36px;
            height: 36px;
            object-fit: contain;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 5px rgba(255,180,0,0.3));
        }

        /* 装备卡片 */
        .equip-card {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); /* 加深卡片背景，提高对比度 */
            padding: 8px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08); /* 稍微加强边框 */
            flex-shrink: 0;
            backdrop-filter: blur(4px); /* 添加背景模糊，防止被背景网格干扰 */
        }

        .equip-icon {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background: #2a2a2a;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 4px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); /* 默认边框 */
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        /* 稀有度边框颜色 - 支持多种可能的Key格式 */
        .rarity-1, .rarity-Key_1, .rarity-equip_rarity_1, .rarity-rarity_1 { border-color: #8e8e8e !important; } /* 1星 - 灰色 */
        .rarity-2, .rarity-Key_2, .rarity-equip_rarity_2, .rarity-rarity_2 { border-color: #4b8e3a !important; } /* 2星 - 绿色 */
        .rarity-3, .rarity-Key_3, .rarity-equip_rarity_3, .rarity-rarity_3 { border-color: #3b88c3 !important; } /* 3星 - 蓝色 */
        .rarity-4, .rarity-Key_4, .rarity-equip_rarity_4, .rarity-rarity_4 { border-color: #9254de !important; } /* 4星 - 紫色 */
        .rarity-5, .rarity-Key_5, .rarity-equip_rarity_5, .rarity-rarity_5 { border-color: #ffb400 !important; } /* 5星 - 金色/橙色 */
        .rarity-6, .rarity-Key_6, .rarity-equip_rarity_6, .rarity-rarity_6 { border-color: #ff4d4f !important; } /* 6星 - 红色/顶级 */

        .equip-info { display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
        .equip-name { font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; }
        .equip-lv { font-size: 11px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); margin-top: 2px; }

        /* 技能列表 */
        .skill-list { 
            display: flex; 
            flex-direction: column; 
            gap: 6px; 
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        
        .skill-item {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
            padding: 6px 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .skill-icon { width: 28px; height: 28px; flex-shrink: 0; }
        .skill-name { font-size: 12px; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; }
        .skill-level { font-size: 11px; margin-left: auto; color: #ffb400; font-weight: bold; flex-shrink: 0; }

        /* 装备网格布局 */
        .equip-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 10px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        
        .equip-grid .equip-card {
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 12px 5px;
            height: 120px;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .equip-grid .equip-icon {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .equip-grid .equip-info {
            align-items: center;
            width: 100%;
        }

        /* 底部装饰信息栏 */
        .char-extra-info {
            margin-top: auto;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 15px;
            border-left: 3px solid #ffb400;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .extra-title {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .extra-content {
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            font-style: italic;
        }


    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="main">
        <div class="bg-decoration">
            <div class="bg-grid"></div>
            <div class="bg-glow-1"></div>
            <div class="bg-glow-2"></div>
            <div class="bg-line" style="top: 20%; opacity: 0.3;"></div>
            <div class="bg-line" style="bottom: 30%; opacity: 0.2;"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- 左侧：基础属性 & 武器 -->
        <div class="side-panel left-panel">
            <div class="section-title">基础状态</div>
            <div class="level-potential">
                <div class="lv-box">
                    <span class="lv-label">等级</span>
                    <span class="lv-val">{{.Char.Level}}</span>
                </div>
                <img class="potential-icon-large" src="/assets/box/Potential_{{.Char.PotentialLevel}}.png" onerror="this.style.display='none'">
            </div>

            <div class="section-title">武器装备</div>
            {{if .Char.Weapon.WeaponData.Name}}
            <div class="equip-card">
                <img class="equip-icon rarity-{{.Char.Weapon.WeaponData.Rarity.Key}}" src="{{.Char.Weapon.WeaponData.IconURL}}">
                <div class="equip-info">
                    <div class="equip-name">{{.Char.Weapon.WeaponData.Name}}</div>
                    <div class="equip-lv">精炼 {{.Char.Weapon.RefineLevel}} / 等级 {{.Char.Weapon.Level}}</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            {{else}}
            <div class="equip-card" style="opacity: 0.5;">未装备武器</div>
            {{end}}

            <div class="section-title">战术道具</div>
            {{if .Char.TacticalItem.TacticalItemData.Name}}
            <div class="equip-card">
                <img class="equip-icon rarity-{{.Char.TacticalItem.TacticalItemData.Rarity.Key}}" src="{{.Char.TacticalItem.TacticalItemData.IconURL}}">
                <div class="equip-info">
                    <div class="equip-name">{{.Char.TacticalItem.TacticalItemData.Name}}</div>
                    <div class="equip-lv">{{.Char.TacticalItem.TacticalItemData.ActiveEffectType.Value}}</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            {{else}}
            <div class="equip-card" style="opacity: 0.5;">未装备战术道具</div>
            {{end}}

            <div class="section-title">技能等级</div>
            <div class="skill-list">
                {{range .Char.CharData.Skills}}
                <div class="skill-item">
                    <img class="skill-icon" src="{{.IconURL}}">
                    <div class="skill-name">{{.Name}}</div>
                    {{$skillId := .ID}}
                    {{with index $.Char.UserSkills $skillId}}
                    <div class="skill-level">Lvl.{{.Level}}</div>
                    {{end}}
                </div>
                {{end}}
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 中间：立绘 -->
        <div class="center-panel">
            <div class="illustration-container">
                <img class="illustration" src="{{.Char.CharData.IllustrationURL}}" alt="{{.Char.CharData.Name}}">
            </div>
            <div class="char-base-info">
                <div class="char-name">{{.Char.CharData.Name}}</div>
                <div class="char-tags">
                    <span class="tag">{{.Char.CharData.Profession.Value}}</span>
                    <span class="tag">{{.Char.CharData.Property.Value}}</span>
                    <span class="tag">{{.Char.CharData.Rarity.Value}}★</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 右侧：装备集成 -->
        <div class="side-panel right-panel">
            <div class="section-title">集成设备情况</div>
            
            <div class="equip-grid">
                <!-- 躯干 -->
                {{if .Char.BodyEquip.EquipData.Name}}
                <div class="equip-card">
                    <img class="equip-icon rarity-{{.Char.BodyEquip.EquipData.Rarity.Key}}" src="{{.Char.BodyEquip.EquipData.IconURL}}">
                    <div class="equip-info">
                        <div class="equip-name">{{.Char.BodyEquip.EquipData.Name}}</div>
                        <div class="equip-lv">躯干 Lv.{{.Char.BodyEquip.EquipData.Level.Value}}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                {{else}}
                <div class="equip-card" style="opacity: 0.5;">
                    <div class="equip-name">躯干</div>
                    <div class="equip-lv">尚未集成</div>
                </div>
                {{end}}

                <!-- 手臂 -->
                {{if .Char.ArmEquip.EquipData.Name}}
                <div class="equip-card">
                    <img class="equip-icon rarity-{{.Char.ArmEquip.EquipData.Rarity.Key}}" src="{{.Char.ArmEquip.EquipData.IconURL}}">
                    <div class="equip-info">
                        <div class="equip-name">{{.Char.ArmEquip.EquipData.Name}}</div>
                        <div class="equip-lv">手臂 Lv.{{.Char.ArmEquip.EquipData.Level.Value}}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                {{else}}
                <div class="equip-card" style="opacity: 0.5;">
                    <div class="equip-name">手臂</div>
                    <div class="equip-lv">尚未集成</div>
                </div>
                {{end}}

                <!-- 饰品1 -->
                {{if .Char.FirstAccessory.EquipData.Name}}
                <div class="equip-card">
                    <img class="equip-icon rarity-{{.Char.FirstAccessory.EquipData.Rarity.Key}}" src="{{.Char.FirstAccessory.EquipData.IconURL}}">
                    <div class="equip-info">
                        <div class="equip-name">{{.Char.FirstAccessory.EquipData.Name}}</div>
                        <div class="equip-lv">饰品1 Lv.{{.Char.FirstAccessory.EquipData.Level.Value}}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                {{else}}
                <div class="equip-card" style="opacity: 0.5;">
                    <div class="equip-name">饰品1</div>
                    <div class="equip-lv">尚未集成</div>
                </div>
                {{end}}

                <!-- 饰品2 -->
                {{if .Char.SecondAccessory.EquipData.Name}}
                <div class="equip-card">
                    <img class="equip-icon rarity-{{.Char.SecondAccessory.EquipData.Rarity.Key}}" src="{{.Char.SecondAccessory.EquipData.IconURL}}">
                    <div class="equip-info">
                        <div class="equip-name">{{.Char.SecondAccessory.EquipData.Name}}</div>
                        <div class="equip-lv">饰品2 Lv.{{.Char.SecondAccessory.EquipData.Level.Value}}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                {{else}}
                <div class="equip-card" style="opacity: 0.5;">
                    <div class="equip-name">饰品2</div>
                    <div class="equip-lv">尚未集成</div>
                </div>
                {{end}}
            </div>

            <div class="char-extra-info">
                <div class="extra-title">Administrator Protocol</div>
                <div class="extra-content">
                    "塔卫二的未来取决于每一个深思熟虑的决策。协议已启动，正在实时监控所有集成设备的能量流向。"
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
